   <body>
      <p>Payout Schedules are generated for every period for the programâ€™s lifespan. For example, if the Billing Frequency is Monthly and the program is setup for two years, there will be 24 Billing Schedules generated when the program is activated.</p>
      <p>Billing Schedules have their own life cycle and are affected by the program life cycle.</p>
      <p>
         <fig>
            <image height="198"
                   placement="break"
                   width="700"
                   href="../attachments/102432692/102432747.png"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>Payout Schedule Status</p>
      <p>
         <table>
            <tgroup cols="3">
               <colspec colname="col1"/>
               <colspec colname="col2"/>
               <colspec colname="col3"/>
               <thead>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Status</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Transition</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Description</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Pending</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>When Schedule is activated</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Future Period</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Open</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Date driven from Pending</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Current period: start date &lt; today &lt; end date + grace period Calculations are ongoing</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Ready</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Date driven from Open</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Period is available for a downstream gathering of results: today &gt; end date + grace period</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Closed</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Event driven from Ready</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Downstream processes have locked the period for audit/reference purposes.</p>
                        <p>All related Aggregated Results are closed</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </p>
      <p>Aggregated and detail calculation results are associated with Open and Ready schedules. Schedules with a Ready status indicate that calculation is no longer occurring, and results are Ready to be sent to or picked up by downstream applications. After the calculated result is consumed, statuses are updated to Closed. For Billing program results, when the invoice is approved, statuses are updated.</p>
      <p>Calculation Result Status</p>
      <p>
         <table>
            <tgroup cols="3">
               <colspec colname="col1"/>
               <colspec colname="col2"/>
               <colspec colname="col3"/>
               <thead>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Status</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Transition</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Description</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Open</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Container schedule becomes Active</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Aggregated Results are calculated based on calculation frequency while the Schedule is Open.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Ready</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Container schedule becomes Ready</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Aggregated Results are not calculated automatically anymore. Container schedule is Ready.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Closed</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Event driven</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Downstream application has updated Aggregated Results as immutable. For example, the related Invoice has been processed, or Payment created.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </p>
